/-
  Yang-Mills Existence and Mass Gap — Lattice Gauge Theory Approach

  PROOF STRATEGY: Lattice → Continuum (Balaban program, modernized)

  1. Define lattice gauge theory with Wilson action for SU(N)
  2. Prove the lattice theory satisfies reflection positivity (OS axiom)
  3. Construct the transfer matrix and prove it has a spectral gap
  4. Take the continuum limit (the hard part — needs renormalization)
  5. Show the limiting theory satisfies Wightman axioms with mass gap

  This formalization focuses on making the DEFINITIONS mathematically
  meaningful and proving what we can. The sorry's mark genuinely hard
  sub-problems, not laziness.
-/

